---
/** ConsultancyProcess — exact copy of S06ProcessGrid with consultancy card text */
---

<!-- Section 06 — Process Grid | Figma: fileKey=RxueMLDFnpgheWZp4MVk7f nodeId=8:276 -->
<section data-figma-ref="8:276" class="bg-light-gray py-20 sm:py-28 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-[1232px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section label (right-aligned) -->
    <div class="flex justify-end">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-text mb-4">How it works</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-end mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <div class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-accent"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Heading -->
    <h2 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl leading-tight mb-12 sm:mb-16 max-w-2xl">
      What happens when you work with me.
    </h2>

    <!-- 2x2 grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Card 1 — Statement Review -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0113.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 00-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 00-9-9z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl mb-3">Statement Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
          I look at what you're paying, line by line. Most owners have never had anyone actually explain their merchant statement to them. I will.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 — System Check -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.288 15.038a5.25 5.25 0 017.424 0M5.106 11.856c3.807-3.808 9.98-3.808 13.788 0M1.924 8.674c5.565-5.565 14.587-5.565 20.152 0M12 20.5h.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl mb-3">System Check</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Your till, your card machine, your broadband, your contract terms. I check whether it all works together and where the weak points are.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 — Recommendation -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl mb-3">Recommendation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
          If something needs changing, I'll tell you what, why, and what it'll cost. If your deal's already fair, we're done.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4 — I Stick Around -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 01-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 00-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 002.25 4.5v2.25z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="w-8 h-0.5 bg-accent mb-6"></div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-medium text-dark text-xl mb-3">I Stick Around</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-text text-sm leading-relaxed">
          This is where most providers disappear. I don't. You get my mobile number. If something breaks mid-service, you ring me and I sort it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
